Class SVXIntegerToBooleanConsumerWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • ccre.channel.AbstractUpdatingInput
      • svx.SVXConsumerWrapper
        • svx.SVXIntegerToBooleanConsumerWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ccre.channel.BooleanInput, ccre.channel.UpdatingInput, com.mentor.systems.svx.ISVXNotification, java.io.Serializable

    public class SVXIntegerToBooleanConsumerWrapper
extends SVXConsumerWrapper
implements ccre.channel.BooleanInput
    A workaround for the fact that Boolean consumers will crash the JVM if their get() method is called. Uses an integer conusmer whose value is converted to an integer.
    Author:
    tthompso
